{"tid":2233444,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"親情與愛情","createTime":"2020-10-07T06:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T11:41:56.000Z","uid":2470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a61926f8d76a3acb57c9a544abd49d6e32528945","tid":2233444,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"兩個人係埋一齊好耐好耐<br />\n其實愛情耐左係咪一定會變親情？<br />\n會冇左感覺，係咪兩樣真係分得咁清楚？<br />\n<br />\n歸左0既愛情 係咪好難變番有？<br />\n大家一齊經歷咁多年<br />\n係咪一下子話無就無？"},{"pid":"96fd73ac0ddbf9d5d000c9e04acf86124abd571b","tid":2233444,"uid":242102,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"變親情係好令人感動嘅事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903c85a77b087875a730f39bf3f82fd137f27d5b","tid":2233444,"uid":2470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"同老婆一齊拍拖十年<br />\n係佢口中話已經冇左愛情<br />\n得番親情<br />\n呢家分居緊。做番朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df676ed720dbcee35ddc83904c5fa7e5814391da","tid":2233444,"uid":224058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"大家需要既野唔同"},{"pid":"afddc7231ae921feed143b047369e5a13b47fab0","tid":2233444,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"我好努力維繫<br />\n但好似做咩都拉唔到佢番轉頭<br />\n<br />\n好似早排結婚記念日<br />\n我送好多小禮物 帶佢食好西<br />\n<br />\n佢話個感覺好勉強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女人其實係咪簡單講需要安全感 需要被愛<br />\n佢話結左婚一直都冇家既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n錢銀我地一直都唔缺<br />\n搞到呢個地步我好後悔<br />\n見完婚姻輔導都冇用咁"},{"pid":"2dcc5299975ac5ef4b0da949edc7f4bfee70a7df","tid":2233444,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"女人好似好簡單<br />\n但又好複雜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定係我諗得太簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6912dd8f295f2fb05e7404588717aca41aa2f6ef","tid":2233444,"